    • engineAdded

      void engineAdded(ScriptEngineWrapper scriptEngineWrapper)
      Called after an engine is added.

      The UI should display the contents of the selected script if it's targeting the added engine.

      Parameters:
      scriptEngineWrapper - the engine that was removed
      Since:
      2.4.0

    • engineRemoved

      void engineRemoved(ScriptEngineWrapper scriptEngineWrapper)
      Called after an engine is removed.

      The UI should clear the contents of the selected script if it's targeting the removed engine.

      Parameters:
      scriptEngineWrapper - the engine that was removed
      Since:
      2.4.0

      default void displayScript(ScriptWrapper script, boolean allowFocus)
      Displays the provided script with/without focusing on it. By default, this method delegates to displayScript(ScriptWrapper).
      Parameters:
      script - The script to be displayed.
      allowFocus - true to allow focusing on the script display, false otherwise.
      Since:
      2.14.0
